General.Name: Rolling Optics Holding AB (publ)
General.Description: Rolling Optics Holding AB (publ) provides secure visual anti-counterfeit solutions based on complex and patented micro-optical technology in Sweden. Its products are primarily self-adhesive labels, which are used in fast-moving consumer goods, spirits and beverages, cosmetics and personal care, packaging, and industrial applications. The company was incorporated in 1952 and is based in Solna, Sweden.
